’Щ@576ce7bec6f5b7deb2710cf5eabb399059bb15b50e923c3c4391d843d0637b04ЪeTitle: title: bytes replace
Path: Examples
Content:
Find and replace contents.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[10 AA FF AA FF] | bytes replace 0x[10 AA] 0x[FF]
Length: 4 (0x4) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff ff aa ff                                          Г—Г—Г—Г—


```
Find and replace all occurrences of find binary.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[10 AA 10 BB 10] | bytes replace --all 0x[10] 0x[A0]
Length: 5 (0x5) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   a0 aa a0 bb  a0                                      Г—Г—Г—Г—Г—


```
Find and replace all occurrences of find binary in table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[ColA ColB ColC]; [0x[11 12 13] 0x[14 15 16] 0x[17 18 19]]] | bytes replace --all 0x[11] 0x[13] ColA ColC
